title: Sawbones: Cavities
description:
Dr. Sydnee finally took a much belated trip to the dentists office and she and Justin are celebrating in the only way they know how: Digging through all the retched ways we've tried to fix teeth since the dawn of time.

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
